---
title: Chipotle BBQ Chicken Cutlets with a Potato, Pepper, Onion & Cilantro Hash
description: This week, we’re bringing barbecue vibes indoors so you can enjoy all the flavors of a cookout any day of the week, any time of year. Chicken cutlets are slathered with a smoky, chipotle-spiked BBQ sauce, then roasted until sticky and juicy. It’s all served over an easy hash of tender roasted potatoes, green pepper, and onion tossed with lime zest and cilantro. And, because we can never have enough barbecue, the chicken’s drizzled with more of the sauce for good measure. Now that’s a dinner win.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chipotle-bbq-chicken-cutlets-fe1c76a9.jpg
